### Get all contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get single contact (valid id) – replace after creating
@contactId = 000000000000000000000000
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Invalid id format (should return 400 or 404 depending on your handler)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/notavalidid
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create contact (POST) – copy the returned id into @contactId above
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
